	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64521313"><p>Small claims court would be the appropriate venue.</p><p>-No attorney representation is allowed, by either party.<br>-Filing fees are ~$50 and commonly waived for those who can't afford it.<br>-The paperwork is a simple fill-in-the-blanks format.<br>-Judges don't accept bullshit "it's in the fineprint of the terms-and-conditions" excuses:  They expect <i>a clear answer in common language</i> as to why the actions should be permissible.<br>-Most small claims court actions are resolved by a judge within a few weeks of initial filing.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64521313">
